OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fdry and cloudy with some mist and fog
OL,7,Fpatches. Some clearer spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping early on Sunday morning.
OL,9,FLight northerly winds turning
OL,10,Fsoutherly overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with some showers
OL,13,Fdeveloping, these will be mostly light
OL,14,Fbut a few sharper showers possible in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon, brighter spells inland.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fwith showers on Monday, winds
OL,19,Fremaining light. A mix of bright or
OL,20,Fsunny spells and cloud on Tuesday and
OL,21,FWednesday.
